Package: evo3D
Title: Structure-Informed Selection Analysis of Protein-Coding Regions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brad", "Broyles", email = "bbroyle@purdue.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a pipeline for structure-aware selection analysis of protein-coding regions. 
    Includes patch-level MSA subsetting, structure alignment, and selection metrics like nucleotide 
    diversity and Tajima's D. Designed for easy use with experimental or predicted protein structures.
